<doc docid='bbc_140813_dwi_ebola_math' lang='ind' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/indonesia/bahasa_inggris/2014/08/140813_dwi_ebola_math' term='ebola'>
Germany asks citizens to leave Ebola affected West Africa
